<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Void | Productivity in the Storm</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body { background-color: #020617; color: #f1f5f9; min-height: 100vh; overflow-x: hidden; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        .rain { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; z-index: 0; pointer-events: none; }
        .drop { position: absolute; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); width: 1px; height: 100px; animation: fall 1.2s linear infinite; }
        @keyframes fall { to { transform: translateY(100vh); } }
        .glass { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); }
        .glow { box-shadow: 0 0 40px -10px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); }
        .text-gradient { background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #fff, #94a3b8); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="flex flex-col items-center">
    <div class="rain"></div>
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-6xl px-6 pt-24 pb-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 mb-6 text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase rounded-full glass text-blue-400 border-blue-500/20">
            System Version 1.0.4 // Active
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tighter text-gradient">THE VOID</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl opacity-60 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">
            Focus isn't found, it's forged. Enter a workspace designed for the deep night, where every task is a commitment to the craft.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="/auth/register" class="px-10 py-4 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl transition-all shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/20 hover:scale-105">
                Initialize Workspace
            </a>
            <a href="/auth/login" class="px-10 py-4 glass hover:bg-white/10 text-white font-bold rounded-2xl transition-all hover:scale-105">
                Access Terminal
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Features Grid -->
    <main class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl glow">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-blue-500/20">
                    <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono">01</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Terminal Tasks</h3>
                <p class="opacity-50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    A minimalist task management engine. Prioritize objectives and deploy solutions without the clutter of traditional tools.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl glow">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-purple-500/20">
                    <span class="text-purple-400 font-mono">02</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Streak Persistence</h3>
                <p class="opacity-50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Consistency is tracked in real-time. Build your streak through completed sessions and watch your progress burn bright.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl glow">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-emerald-500/20">
                    <span class="text-emerald-400 font-mono">03</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Audit Intel</h3>
                <p class="opacity-50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Every action is logged in our secure audit trail. Complete transparency on your productivity sessions and security.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 4 -->
            <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl glow">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-amber-500/20">
                    <span class="text-amber-400 font-mono">04</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Night Theme</h3>
                <p class="opacity-50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Optimized for late-night sessions. Deep blacks, glassmorphism, and a calming rain effect to keep your focus locked.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 5 -->
            <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl glow">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-rose-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-rose-500/20">
                    <span class="text-rose-400 font-mono">05</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Focus Sessions</h3>
                <p class="opacity-50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Integrate deep-work intervals automatically. Every completed task powers your productivity metrics.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 6 -->
            <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl glow">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-slate-500/20">
                    <span class="text-slate-400 font-mono">06</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Admin Control</h3>
                <p class="opacity-50 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    Scalable hierarchy for team management. Oversee users and system health from a unified command center.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="relative z-10 pb-12 opacity-30 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">
        Built for the storm &copy; 2024 THE VOID
    </footer>

    <script>
        const rain = document.querySelector('.rain');
        for (let i = 0; i < 100; i++) {
            const drop = document.createElement('div');
            drop.classList.add('drop');
            drop.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
            drop.style.animationDuration = Math.random() * 0.5 + 0.7 + 's';
            drop.style.animationDelay = Math.random() * 5 + 's';
            drop.style.opacity = Math.random() * 0.5;
            rain.appendChild(drop);
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>